node.title: 5 officers injured during shooting and standoff at Phoenix home
node.description: Authorities have asked people to stay away from the area.
node.content: ["Five officers are hurt after a \"critical incident\" broke out involving a person barricaded inside a home, Phoenix police said Friday. Police Chief Jeri Williams said one officer is in critical condition, CBS' Phoenix affiliate reports.", "Video showed a man involved in the standoff holding a baby while engaging with officers. Police said that baby was found unharmed.", "The scene of the shooting and standoff is still active hours after it all unfolded around 2 a.m. Authorities are asking people to stay away from the area.\u00a0"]
